'''Kan'us''' is a village in [[Iraq]]. It is located southeast of River [[Tigris]], north of [[Al-Shirqat]], which lies on the western banks of the river, and west of [[Makhmur, Iraq|Makhmur]]. By 2016, Kan'us was under control of [[Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant|ISIL]].

