The [[Commonwealth (United States insular area)|U.S. commonwealth]] of the [[Northern Mariana Islands]] first required its residents to register their [[motor vehicle]]s and display [[license plate]]s in 1944.<ref>http://www.worldlicenseplates.com/world/PA_NMAR.html</ref>
